Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE HERO LOST IN THE GLACIER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish him this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra already took care of the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be a downgrade, but I would lose\Nface if I didn't kill a Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!\NI'll fight to the end alone if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NYou have to avenge Dai, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He died trying to rescue you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!\NDai was defeated because of me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of my recklessness!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I lose my head and get killed fighting,\Nwho's going to rescue Dai?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remember...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a Mage must always be\Nthe most level-headed in the party.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mentor!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do I use what little\NMagic Power I have left?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one thing I can do\Nfor Dai right now is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, little Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I can do is run as far as I can...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and let everyone know what happened!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A wise choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept his cool\Neven after I provoked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. There was another\Nfrom the Hero's party who could fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Beast King's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you my opponent now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Redemption Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The brave Beast King Crocodine\Njust up and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never let a target\Nescape me twice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is beginning to irritate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to abandon Dai and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But... there was nothing else I could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never choose to turn tail\Nunless the situation was severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the sort of man you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I doubt he's unharmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but my Ultra Combustion Slash\Ndidn't find its mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant, Dai focused\Nall his remaining power into an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which defended himself\Nby countering my Combustion Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What combat instincts!\NWhat an unyielding will to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the millennia of battles\Netched in the blood of the Dragon Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the attack he used\Nin that instant was...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigabrake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spell was Raiden\Nand its power was weak...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that was definitely the attack of\Nhis father, General Baran!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He may say he rejects his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but it appears that the shadow of Baran\Nis a great influence on Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die yet, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'd have to question\Nwhy I bothered becoming a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You stupid fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it, Chiu!\N-Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was actually beginning\Nto think you weren't that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you went off\Nand put Dai in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a friend of the Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Chiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no excusing what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologizing won't fix anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chiu, was it?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a fledgling. It's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got enough on his plate\Nsaving his own hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get yourself patched up\Nand get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! D-Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather take a fist to the face\Nthan sympathy from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, you'll have to search for Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai probably fell in the ocean\Nin the far north, northwest of Orzam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's no normal human. I doubt he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got room for someone your size.\NCare to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!\NHow wise of you to bring me along!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Let me come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't for the wounded or children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't search if you can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you have\Nthe Magic Power for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's lost because of me!\NI can't leave this to someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Princess, please!\NYou've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got a spell or something\Nthat can heal Magic Power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a spell like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I give the Papunica Troika some\NMagic Water that heals Magic Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I believe Marin has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he's all fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked to him like that\Non purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it'd be more effective\Nthan yelling at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing from wounds\Ncaused by Dark Aura takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have him being morose\Nwhile I'm stuck in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I need him on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Sometimes it's hard to tell\Nif you guys rely on Popp or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please!\N-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm begging you, Miss Marin!\N-Fine! You can have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm begging you!\N-Okay, now let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-You've got to!\N- I said yes, so let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's worried\Nthat I'm going to outshine him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on, Dai!\NI promise I'm going to rescue you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you just say, Hyunckel?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I said once Dai's safety is confirmed,\Nwe should invade the Dark Army stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle, the enemy's\Nfirst line of defense has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The only remaining\Npillars of the Dark Army
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,are Hadorra, Mystban, and Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fight with\NDark King Ban is drawing near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEAST KING REDEMPTION BLAST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.53,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can assume that Dark King Ban\Nis in the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, what is our course of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with the Disciples of Aban.\NWe should invade the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we defeat them in an invasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We doubt we can defeat them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we can take even one of them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it will bring us that much closer\Nto Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to unite all of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, my fellow world leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bengana, do you object?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I believe\Nwe'd need that boy for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been focused on weapons and arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but when I saw him save us,\NI was honestly in awe.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heroes truly are powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was pounding the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You were worked up\Nlike a child back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona, if he is successfully\Nrescued, I promise to help however I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's friends are searching the icy seas\Nfrom the sky as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But, isn't that close\Nto the enemy stronghold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If memory serves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the Field of Death\Nis a place that even birds avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's because of\Nthe Dark King's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be okay, Dai!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I'm going to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This might take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's time to face King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, I never confirmed Dai's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm almost certain he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't wiped out\Nthe Hero and his friends as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've failed my promise to King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible\NI'll be executed on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to shun you\Nfor your mysterious nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the six Legion Commanders,\Nit's possible that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you were the most sincere with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath that mask of silence you wear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but sense a fiery soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can now face my end with my head high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've powered up greatly,\Njust like King Ban expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be anticlimactic,\Nbut he'll commend you and that'll be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll commend us?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, this was all thanks\Nto my research after all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban, I, Hadorra, have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh!\N-Can it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart feels bright and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the sun shining through\Nthe clouds above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My face has never been seen\Nby anyone but you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I believe revealing it to Hadorra
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best way\Nto express my approval of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this ancient,\Nhaggard face surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King... Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.89,On Top,,0,0,0,,BAN, THE DARK KING
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this truly the King Ban\Nthat I've feared for so long?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense the pressure from him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistaking that immense presence\NI feel through that thin veil.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's so incredibly old!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he really possess the power\Nof a god of the Underworld?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That frail neck...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a Superior Being,\NI could snap it so easily!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to try, Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My King, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've always liked about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That boundless spirit,\Nand heart that believes only in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your recent behavior\Nhad been rather uncharacteristic of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that spirit rekindled within you\Nputs me at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can never beat him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is truly worlds beyond me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As I had hoped,\Nyou have broken through your shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power is now\Nalmost in league with my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby rescind my previous order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to continue your duties\Nas Dark Commander by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may speak, my Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains me to say this\Nafter you have granted me such mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is something I wish to do\Nbefore being reinstated as Dark Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about the Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By any means, I wish to defeat\NDai and the other Disciples of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my final desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you grant me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need for such formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, the Hero, and his allies\Nare the greatest threat to my army.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What objection\Nwould I have to their defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Six Legions are in shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems unnecessary\Nthat you command them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, you will take command.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, you will protect\Nthe Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you won't object to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dai survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then they will surely\Ncome to attack this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To take my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I shall obey, my King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what should I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You will maintain your current role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll continue\Nmy morbid work for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't they mentioned me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mystic Legion and I\Nare still in fighting shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're acting like\NI don't even matter anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I suck up to Hadorra and\Nthe other Legion Commanders for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to distinguish myself\Nto make Dark King Ban acknowledge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What... happened to me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the ice?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My wounds haven't healed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did I survive like this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. You protected me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's warm.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You kept me from being frozen in ice.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A crack!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Hadorra's attack cause that?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You sustained such damage for me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you've been protecting me\Nall this time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get out of here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, would you like\Nsome more servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The game of chess is quite deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thought to be a game of humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was originally\Ninvented by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The beauty of chess{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is in using the five types of pieces with\Ndifferent abilities to protect the king.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pawn moves forward\Nto defeat its enemies.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The knight leaps eight ways,\Nstriking from above.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rook charges horizontally or\Nvertically to decimate foes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bishop glides diagonally\Nlike a phantom.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And, possessing the abilities\Nof both rook and bishop,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the queen is the most powerful piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those pieces made of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Orichalcum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Very observant of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have those five pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had anyone to play with\Nin a long time anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use the Forbidden Magic\Nyou used to create Flazzard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and make those pieces the ultimate force\Nthat would serve with you as their king...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that make things interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's around here! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's somewhere around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:11.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:19.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:26.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:30.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:34.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:38.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:42.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:48.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:53.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:57.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:03.96,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i}
